entered into the following transactions during 2020:
•Debt issuance: On March 16, 2020, the Company issued $3.5 billion of new senior notes. The proceeds of this issuance
were mainly used to pay the consideration for the cash tender and redemption offer as described below. Interest on this debt
is paid semi-annually.
