Additionally, these subsidiaries may be subject to regulatory restrictions on the amount of annual dividends or other distributions
(such as loans or cash advances) that insurance companies may extend to their parent companies without prior approval. As of
December 31, 2020, these amounts, including restricted GAAP net assets of the Company’s subsidiaries, were as follows:
